==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Marconis law
<hw>Mar*co"ni's law</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <fld>(Wireless
Teleg.)</fld> <def>The law that the maximum good signaling distance
varies directly as the square of the height of the transmitting
antenna.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Marconism</ent>⟦br⟧
